lines.text: OFFICE OF THE PRINCIPAL ACCOUNTANT GENERAL (AUDIT), DELHI
डी० जी० ए० सी० आर० भवन, आई. पी. एस्टेट, नई दिल्ली-110002
D.G.A.C.R. BUILDING, I.P. ESTATE, NEW DELHI-110002
Subject: Intimation regarding Joining of Shri Rakesh Mohan as the Pr.
This is to inform that Shri Rakesh Mohan, IA&AS (1987 Batch) has taken over
the charge as the Pr. Accountant General (Audit), Delhi in place of Shri Laisram Angam
As you are aware, under the auspices of the Comptroller and Auditor General
of India, the Pr. Accountant General (Audit), Delhi is responsible for audit of all
expenditure and revenue of all the departments and organizations of the Government of
National Capital Territory of Delhi, including companies and autonomous bodies under
its administrative control. In addition, he is entrusted with the audit of Delhi Police.
This office requests your continuous support and cooperation to our auditing
responsibilities. You may please inform this to all the concerned.
